      "content": "I hear how devastating it is to feel unheard by medical professionals and to be trapped in a state of constant, unrelenting agony. When the pain feels like a fire you cannot escape, the desire to find peace in non-existence is a terrifying and understandable reaction to such unbearable suffering. Please know that your feelings are valid, and your pain is real, even when it feels impossible to manage. You are not alone in feeling this way, and there are compassionate specialists who can help you navigate the complex world of chronic nerve pain. Please consider reaching out to a crisis support line or a mental health professional who can offer immediate support during these overwhelming moments.",
